. The woman’s 11-year-old son was later found unharmed, it said. The mother later travelled to the main station in Duesseldorf, some 35 kilometres away, where she jumped in front of a train, according to Bild. She was rescued from between two track beds and taken to a local hospital for treatment, national news agency DPA reported, citing emergency services. Investigations are ongoing, police said. [AFP] Vanguard News Nigeria. Five children were found dead in an apartment in western Germany on Thursday, police said, with local media reporting they were murdered by their mother who later tried to kill herself as well. The children were found in a private apartment in the city of Solingen in North Rhine-Westphalia state,… September 3, 2020 In "News" A mother in Japan is under investigation for murder after her four children, including a girl as young as three, were found dead at home, Japanese media reports and police said Monday. August 22, 2016 In "News" By Chioma Onuegbu - Uyo ONE Mrs Esther Frank, a mother two and indigene of Anambra state residing in Uyo, Akwa Ibom state capital has committed suicide, leaving a suicide note for her husband and sons. It was gathered that the deceased drank a bottle of sniper on Thursday, April… April 10, 2020 In "Metro"